nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 133 is the 111th issue of the magazine Star Wars Insider and the 41st published by Titan Magazines. It was released on May 1, 2012.

Star Wars Insider goes behind enemy lines to find out what the greatest battles are in the Star Wars saga. Plus, Wicket the Ewok, Willow Ufgood, and now the star of the hit TV Show Life's Too Short, Warwick Davis, drops by to answer your questions.
